data.description: Situated 3rd Tier from pristine #tablerocklake with a 10x24 boat slip(65k) just a couple blocks away sits this adorable, beautifully updated, four bedroom home. Perfectly perched just a few blocks from pristine #tablerocklake, in one of the most sought after, nautical subdivisions (Kimberling Hills), sits this incredible, HGTV inspired retreat! Tucked away on a 1/4 acre lot, this joyfully & skillfully constructed home has adorable curb appeal, XL driveway with carport for all your lake friends, a fenced in yard & low maintenance landscaping that will be welcoming you home each & every glorious day. Love the outdoors? You will adore the simple starlit nights fireside just off the spacious open patio space adorned with towering mature shade trees & the almost ''flat'' fenced-in backyard, perfect for all those furbabies. Want to bring the outdoors in? Large windows invite you through a bright & airy & exceptionally updated, open floor plan from kitchen to living, which includes: a chef's kitchen w/granite, updated cabinetry (tons of storage), stainless appliances(all stay), all open to the living area for grand entertaining, a super cozy wood burning fireplace ready to chase away those winter blues, beautiful & easy to maintain wood laminate & ceramic flooring, HGTV inspired/updated bathrooms, walk-in owner's suite tiled shower, three spacious guest bedrooms (one is so big it could even be a second living), large mudroom/laundry with access to the carport & open storage area. BONUS: complete the total lake house package w/a 10x24 purchase for 65k OR boat slip lease just down the street at the simply amazing Port of Kimberling Marina (with purchase of a 15k boat) Come see what all that Table Rock Lake craze is about @ 6 Edgemont Drive :o)
